reviewText: This is a rip-off for the price and the length of the video!  The visuals are ridiculous and not even amusing to watch.  Don't waste your money . . . or time . . . or expectations on this item!  There is * N O T H I N G * CONTAINED IN THIS ITEM!
This is for my mother, who loves ballet. I'm not a fan, and she has no computer. I am sorry.
